{
  "stem": "14060.6",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What we we considered was lucky that he got out of the Munka Tabor, and he never went into it, became a disaster afterwards because he got deported.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So it was really a vicious circle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, the, the, the period of the mid-40s, you must understand that, for instance, my father in a couple of properties which we had, which were permanent properties in the city, had a cinema advertising board, which entitled us-- they gave us packs of tickets-- to any performance.",
      "word_count": 48
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And even if it was a full house, they put in two chairs.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Anytime, we could go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Till this day, I'm not a keen cinema goer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I go what interests me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But I was never a child who needed to do some tricks to get to the cinema because all I had to do was to go to the wardrobe or, or in the drawer and take out as many tickets as I wanted.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had-- But the reason I'm telling you that is there were two cinemas in town and a very large theatre, which my mother used to take me.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That the propaganda films of the Germans-- which was played in German because in our town they didn't even have to translate it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "You know, didn't have to have subtitles on it-- were absolutely unbelievably effective.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You know, some of the films-- I forget the name of it-- where Jews are compared to rats, you know, in their disgusting manner.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Now, this brutalizing of the Jews was systematically fed all through the war.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And they didn't need really a lot of prompting, I must say.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So this is another little anecdote which I can add to it.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
